s/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-partygoer-was-misidentified-as-hamas-terrorist-on-oct-7-killed-by-israeli-forces/0000018d-d14f-df79-a5cd-f17f934d0000</guid></item><item><title>MAD in Lebanon：我们是否正在走向相互毁灭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mad-in-lebanon-are-we-on-our-way-to-mutual-assured-destruction/0000018d-d06d-d3b8-af9f-dbeda6b60000</link><description>以色列有能力对黎巴嫩造成大规模破坏，但这种破坏会发生在双方身上；这种情况仍然可以避免</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mad-in-lebanon-are-we-on-our-way-to-mutual-assured-destruction/0000018d-d06d-d3b8-af9f-dbeda6b60000</guid></item><item><title>普京、内塔尼亚胡和特朗普：撒谎、危险的三人组</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/putin-netanyahu-and-trump-a-lying-dangerous-trio/0000018d-d0f4-d06c-abbd-d8f4021b0000</link><description>弗拉基米尔·普京、唐纳德·特朗普和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的政治体系截然不同，但三人都渴望通过无休止的谎言和对现实的另类解释来让人民感到疲倦和压抑，从而屈服。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 15:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/putin-netanyahu-and-trump-a-lying-dangerous-trio/0000018d-d0f4-d06c-abbd-d8f4021b0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列工作场所中阿拉伯人和犹太人关系的研究表明，10 月 7 日和加沙战争之后，信任度急剧下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/trust-has-declined-the-disturbing-data-on-relations-between-arabs-and-jews-at-work-in/0000018d-d103-d398-a5ff-f347616c0000</link><description>一项新的研究发现，犹太人与受过高等教育的阿拉伯人一起工作的意愿显着下降，以色列阿拉伯人在大多数犹太工作场所工作的意愿显着下降，但仍有理由乐观</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/trust-has-declined-the-disturbing-data-on-relations-between-arabs-and-jews-at-work-in/0000018d-d103-d398-a5ff-f347616c0000</guid></item><item><title>难道这些享有特权的白人就不能同情被哈马斯杀害的以色列人吗？</title><link>http