/description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:04:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-live/rocket-sirens-sound-in-eilat-u-k-weighs-suspending-arms-exports-to-israel/0000018d-cef4-df79-a5cd-eefe9ca40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的命运取决于统治加沙的巴勒斯坦人和哈马斯的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/the-fate-of-the-israeli-hostages-depends-on-palestinians-running-gaza-and-hamas-future/0000018d-cd71-d101-a3dd-fdf333c20000</link><description>在埃及和卡塔尔的援助下，加沙地带的战后重建取决于巴勒斯坦政权的建立，至少目前还取决于叶海亚·辛瓦尔的同意 — — 而哈马斯中没有人足够强大来告诉他该做什么</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/the-fate-of-the-israeli-hostages-depends-on-palestinians-running-gaza-and-hamas-future/0000018d-cd71-d101-a3dd-fdf333c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承认：14个北部社区撤离“是为了让以色列国防军能够自由行动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-14-northern-communities-evacuated-to-give-idf-forces-freedom-of-operation/0000018d-cd72-d101-a3dd-fdf330960000</link><description>在回应高等法院的请愿书时，该州写道，疏散决定是基于操作考虑——尽管政府当时表示“无法确保民众的安全”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-14-northern-communities-evacuated-to-give-idf-forces-freedom-of-operation/0000018d-cd72-d101-a3dd-fdf330960000</guid></item><item><title>网络攻击后以色列国家档案馆网站的未来“不确定”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/future-of-israels-state-archive-website-uncertain-following-cyberattack/0000018d-cd33-d914-a5ad-cf33dfd90000</link><description>官员们表示，这个问题要到今年年底才能解决，届时人们期待已久的新档案网站将启动，但一位前首席档案管理员对新网站的工作无法在截止日期前完成表示担忧。一位研究人员表示，长期关闭对研究、文化和公共话语造成了前所未有的损害。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/future-of-israels-state-archive-website-uncertain-following-cyberattack/0000018d-cd33-d914-a5ad-cf33dfd90000</guid></item><item><title>国家向最高法院表示：如果四月份征兵法未通过，正统派将被征召入伍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/state-to-top-court-haredim-will-be-drafted-if-conscription-law-isnt-passed-by-april/0000018d-cd43-d2b4-a9bf-cf77a2cb0000</link><description>三月底是新军队草案立法的最后日期。以色列政府告诉最高法院，如果以色列政府届时未能颁布新法律，“政府不征召犹太学院学生就没有法律依据”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 21:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/state-to-top-court-haredim-will-be-drafted-if-conscription-law-isnt-passed-by-april/0000018d-cd43-d2b4-a9bf-cf77a2cb0000</guid></item><item><title>著名的艾什·哈托拉拉比因涉嫌多年性侵犯未成年人而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/well-known-aish-hatorah-rabbi-arrested-on-suspicion-of-sexually-assaulting-minor-for-years/0000018d-cd00-d606-a79d-dddf11020000</link><description>美国犹太圈子里的知名人物、艾什·哈托拉组织创始人的儿子拉比·耶胡达·温伯格 (Rabbi Yehuda Weinberg) 被指控在 20 年前性侵一名 10 岁至 15 岁的女性亲戚。他否认了这些指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 19:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/well-known-aish-hatorah-rabbi-arrested-on-suspicion-of-sexually-assaulting-minor-for-years/0000018d-cd00-d606-a79d-dddf11020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回撤销本-格维尔部长任命的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-rejects-petition-to-nullify-ben-gvirs-appointment/0000018d-cd12-deb3-afdd-ffb289cc0000</link><description>高等法院裁定，没有理由干预内塔尼亚胡总理选择伊塔马尔·本-格维尔担任以色列国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 19:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-rejects-petition-to-nullify-ben-gvirs-appointment/0000018d-cd12-deb3-afdd-ffb289cc0000</guid></item><item><title>以